---
const features = [
  {
    title: "Build for Profit",
    description:
      "Launch products, find customers, and build a business. Bet on an idea and see if it sticks.",
    icon: "💰",
  },
  {
    title: "Build for Impact",
    description:
      "Solve real problems for your community. Ship tools that help people, not just your portfolio.",
    icon: "🌍",
  },
  {
    title: "Build for Craft",
    description:
      "Learn by doing. Ship side projects, experiment with new tech, and grow as a builder.",
    icon: "🛠️",
  },
];
---

<section class="relative py-20 sm:py-32 bg-white" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center">
      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-primary-600">
        Why Join?
      </h2>
      <p
        class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl"
      >
        Three reasons builders bet on themselves
      </p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
        Not every bet is about money. Some builders ship to earn, others
        to make a difference, others to grow. All of them belong here.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-none">
      <dl
        class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3"
      >
        {
          features.map((feature) => (
            <div class="flex flex-col">
              <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
                <div class="h-12 w-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary-50">
                  <span class="text-2xl">{feature.icon}</span>
                </div>
                {feature.title}
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
                <p class="flex-auto">{feature.description}</p>
              </dd>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
